These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: amber, orange, mauve, light-blue, red, chestnut
1. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |       2        |     3     |      4       |   5   |   6    |
| Color   | orange | red | amber | chestnut | light-blue | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, lemonade, juice, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |   5    |    6    |
| Beverage   | juice | 7up | lemonade | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | fanta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-3::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, car, tram, jet-ski, roller, quad-bike
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5       |       6       |
| Transport   | car | tram | roller | airplane | quad-bike | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: surfing, rugby, basketball, golf, snowboarding, baseball
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |   3    |    4    |      5      |  6  |
| Sport   | basketball | surfing | baseball | rugby | snowboarding | golf |

