3. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |   5    |  6  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | fantasy | action | crime | superhero | spy |

