2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |     4     |   5    |    6    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | pony | rabbit | bird | hamster | chinchilla |

