.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-19::.
6 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, billiard, canasta, poker, mah-jongg
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |  3   |    4    |     5      |   6   |
| Game   | billiard | canasta | poker | mah-jongg | backgammon | snooker |

