.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-20::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, hot-chocolate, coffee, almond-milk, lemonade
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4      |      5      |   6   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | lemonade | almond-milk | fanta | coffee |

 